# ✅ Smart Task Manager

A productivity web application that helps users manage weekly and monthly tasks with automatic weekly reset functionality and completion tracking.

![HTML5](https://img.shields.io/badge/HTML5-E34F26?style=for-the-badge&logo=html5&logoColor=white)
![CSS3](https://img.shields.io/badge/CSS3-1572B6?style=for-the-badge&logo=css3&logoColor=white)
![JavaScript](https://img.shields.io/badge/JavaScript-F7DF1E?style=for-the-badge&logo=javascript&logoColor=black)

---

## 🚀 About

A clean, intuitive task manager built to help you stay on top of your weekly and monthly goals. Features automatic weekly resets so you always start fresh, with a history of what you've accomplished.

---

## ✨ Features

- ➕ **Add Tasks** — quickly create tasks with title, priority, and due date
- ✅ **Mark Complete** — check off tasks as you finish them
- 🔄 **Weekly Auto Reset** — tasks automatically reset every week
- 📅 **Monthly Tracking** — view completion rate over the month
- 📊 **Progress Dashboard** — visual overview of completed vs pending tasks
- 💾 **Local Storage** — tasks persist even after closing the browser
- 🎨 **Priority Labels** — color-coded High / Medium / Low priority

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Frontend | HTML5, CSS3, Vanilla JavaScript |
| Storage | LocalStorage API |
| Styling | Custom CSS with Flexbox/Grid |

---

## ⚙️ How to Run

No installation needed! Just open in a browser:

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/Task-manager.git
cd Task-manager

# Open directly in browser
open index.html
```

Or visit the live demo: **[Live Demo Link](#)**

